37,000 U.S. troops stationed on the territory of South Korea,
saying it was necessary to defend the security interests of the
United States.
</P>
<P>
"If circumstances warrant that we go back to square one we
can do so without damage to our interests. If circumstances
require that we go down a different road altogether we will do
so to defend our interests," she said. 
