<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, September 18 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange closed at 1763.13 on Saturday, up 1.08 pints
from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 1,918,458 shares changed hands in 825 deals, and the
turnover was 5.46 billion rials (about 1.82 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
In the trading, shares of 39 companies made gains, and those of
16 others declined. 
</P>
