<HEADLINE> China to Increase Import and Export Of Cosmetics </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, September 18 (Xinhua) -- China opened an
international cosmetics fair today here in Guangzhou, capital of
south China's Guangdong Province, to increase export and import of
cosmetics.
</P>
<P>
