<HEADLINE> Six Killed in Tanzanian Road Accident </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, September 18 (Xinhua) -- Six people died on spot
and 10 others were injured after a semi-trailer lorry rammed into
two stationed lorries on Thursday midnight in Coast Region in east
Tanzania, Daily News said Saturday.
</P>
