a specially equipped aircraft from South Africa to conduct the
food drops that so far have been performed by Royal Australian Air
Force (RAAF) C-130 transport aircraft.
</P>
<P>
He said the U.N. planned to use the special aircraft for high
altitude "snow-dropping" of individual 200-gram packets of
high-protein biscuits.
</P>
<P>
Two RAAF aircraft Friday delivered 20 tons of rice to three
different areas of East Timor.
</P>
<P>
Wimhurst said the humanitarian situation in certain areas of
East Timor remained serious and the air dropping of food was only
a temporary solution until proper food deliveries could be
arranged on the ground. 
