</P>
<P>
The Chinese youth delegation was led by Zhao Yufen, a well
known Chinese scientist, while the media delegation comprises
representatives of Xinhua News Agency and Beijing-based major
Chinese newspapers.
</P>
<P>
During their stay here, the Chinese delegations will call on
President Rafiq Tarar, Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif and other
high-ranking government ministers. 
</P>
</TEXT>
